<title>It's Jesus I really want to see</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Det er Jesus jeg ønsker å få se
 Det er Jesus jeg ønsker å få se!
 Jo mer jeg ser av denne jord,
 dess mindre den betyr!
 For det er Jesus
 jeg ønsker å få se.

[V2]
 It's Jesus I really want to see
 It's Jesus I really want to see
 The more I see of this world,
 the less it means to me
 for it is Jesus I really want to see.</lyrics>
<key>E</key>
<aka>Det er Jesus</aka>
</song>